data.description: Motivated Seller!! Price reduced $24,000!! Pre-inspected report in MLS. Property management handles this neat and clean duplex!  Lower unit is leased until Sept. '24 & has a 4-season porch that opens to fenced backyard. Furnished upper unit has been great for short term rentals. Currently vacant & can be owner occupied. Concrete parking pad is shared by tenants. Trash, lawn & snow is included in rent.  P/I record available.  Cash flows & 3% assumable loan available for owner occupancy.  Close to medical facilities, downtown, parks & bus line.  Pets allowed in lower unit, $50 mo. extra. Tenants require overnight notice (has pets).
